{"type":"message","id":"f18ef197","parentId":"b72d5b75","timestamp":"2026-06-05T01:00:00.905Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Friday, June 5th, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-05 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1780621200901}}
{"type":"message","id":"832b9855","parentId":"f18ef197","timestamp":"2026-06-05T01:00:07.076Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job reminder that's fired daily. The user wants me to silently confirm I've noted the Cursor collaboration rules. I should just acknowledge this briefly as a cron notification, no need for action here since it's just a reminder/confirmation request."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n📋 规则已确认记住。\n\n**Cursor 协作规则摘要：**\n1. 提交任务 → `submit_task.py --title --instructions --notify`\n2. 用户确认回复 → `confirm_write.py --task-id --decision auto --reply`\n3. 查看队列 → `--list`\n4. 查看结果 → `--results`\n\n以上规则已存在于 AGENTS.md 中，日常自动执行，无需重复提醒。\n\n（静默确认，无其他操作）\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780621200904}}
